Alternative Title:
		Ernesto Zedillo Ponce de León



Ernesto Zedillo
President of Mexico

Also known asErnesto Zedillo Ponce de LeónbornDecember 27, 1951 (age 65)Mexico City, Mexicotitle / officepresident, Mexico (1994-2000)political affiliationInstitutional Revolutionary Party


View Biographies Related To
